    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 287120.0,
      "end_time": 288688.0,
      "text": "These mother falcon companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 288788.0,
      "end_time": 290457.0,
      "text": "dragged an old lady through the mud"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 290557.0,
      "end_time": 292626.0,
      "text": "so that we won't be able to sue them anymore?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 292726.0,
      "end_time": 295462.0,
      "text": "Yeah. This story is insane."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 295562.0,
      "end_time": 298698.0,
      "text": "McDonalds had a policy that almost killed someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 298798.0,
      "end_time": 301100.0,
      "text": "and it took Stella's lawsuit to change it."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 301101.0,
      "end_time": 302936.0,
      "text": "She should be considered a hero."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 303360.0,
      "end_time": 306406.0,
      "text": "But because of the companies, we treat her like a punch-line."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 306506.0,
      "end_time": 309808.0,
      "text": "Okay, are you two done talking about civil court cases?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 309910.0,
      "end_time": 312746.0,
      "text": "Because Kendra's case is in criminal court."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 312846.0,
      "end_time": 314414.0,
      "text": "It's a completely different system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 314514.0,
      "end_time": 316616.0,
      "text": "the one I happen to know quite a bit about."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 316716.0,
      "end_time": 318510.0,
      "text": "She has a great case"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 318151.0,
      "end_time": 319753.0,
      "text": "and a jury is gonna be very responsive to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 319853.0,
      "end_time": 322389.0,
      "text": "Oh, they're a ton of problems with jury trials."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 322489.0,
